      <title>泰国和哈萨克斯坦就免签证协议达成协议以促进旅游业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/thailand-kazakhstan-agree-on-visa-waiver-pact-to-boost-tourism</link>
